<div class="container mt-5">
  <div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h1 class="card-title text-center">About the Cryptocurrency Tracker</h1>
      <p class="card-text">
        This application provides up-to-date information on various cryptocurrencies,
        their market prices, market capitalization, and transaction history. Users
        can view detailed information about each cryptocurrency and related transactions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Data Sources</h2>
          <p class="card-text">
            The data for this application is sourced from the CoinRanking API, which
            offers comprehensive and up-to-date information on various cryptocurrencies.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">Database Structure</h2>
          <p class="card-text">
            Below is the Entity-Relationship Diagram (ERD) showing the database structure
            of this application, illustrating how different entities such as Users,
            Cryptocurrencies, and Transactions are interrelated.
          </p>
          <%= image_tag 'crypto.png', alt: 'Cryptocurrency ERD', class: 'img-fluid rounded' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center mt-4">
    <h3>Further Information</h3>
    <p>
      For more details about how this application works or to contribute to its development,
      please visit our GitHub repository or contact the development team.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
